            "text": "Letters - a written adventure",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a charming puzzle-platformer that has the player revisit Sarah's old letters and online \"mysite\" conversations from her childhood and teenage years in order to manipulate words to alter the events. Revisit old friendships, interact with the game's art and enjoy its coming of age story in an adorable, yet sometimes hard-hitting, story.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
