      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The concept behind ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Letters - a written adventure",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is similar to that of the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Scribblenauts",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " series where the player must us words to manipulate their surroundings. However, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Letters",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a much more story-focussed experienced with the surroundings telling a story as you interact directly with the dialogue. It's a clever system that shows the magic behind what video games can achieve.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Not every highlighted word is a means to solve a puzzle and yet, they can be used to interact with drawings and doodles. For example, a lighthouse drawn in one letter can be altered by either combining it with \"Russia\" or \"Switzerland\", which then changes the lighthouse's origins and provides a fun little quote alongside it. These details weren't required by 5AM Games but the extra mile that they've provided establishes a charming personality that is present throughout.  ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "html",
        "html": "<a href=\"https://powera.pxf.io/c/3324894/1309898/15385\" target=\"_top\" id=\"1309898\"><img src=\"//a.impactradius-go.com/display-ad/15385-1309898\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\"/></a><img height=\"0\" width=\"0\" src=\"https://imp.pxf.io/i/3324894/1309898/15385\" style=\"position:absolute;visibility:hidden;\" border=\"0\" />"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Letters",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "'s soundtrack is well implemented and adapts to key shifts within the game's tone. When you're treated to bad news, the music will adapt by matching what's happening on screen, including coming to a grinding halt in order to emphasise key dramatic moments. And this isn't exclusive to the music; the use of colours often highlights the mood of the character, allowing the game's art director to flex their creative muscles.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
